Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by suddenly pouncing on Kakashi-sensei like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrinkly old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This old hag... is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget what you did back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,White Fang of the Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall avenge my son's death by defeating you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... no, you see... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions or answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister... Take a good look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:01:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He resembles him closely, but this one is not the White Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the White Fang of the Leaf died long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you got word of it, you cried tears of regret, since you could not avenge your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha, I was only pretending to have gone senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi-sensei and the rest of you, please stand back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Leaf Medical Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:01.67,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord4\blur4\fax0.18\fad(737,680)\pos(650,546)}The Medical Ninja's Student
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.68,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.65\fax0.1\frz15.794\b1\frx352\fry356\pos(436,228)\c&H969292&}Treatment Room 3{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to have used a heavy metal-based toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the type that acts upon the muscles to destroy the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just from that brief examination...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You could tell that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His medical record please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the list of toxic ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are blank spaces here and there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can predict the general outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The cardiac muscle will be destroyed,\Nand the heart could stop beating at any time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to say whether we can concoct an antidote in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean that!\NIsn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please assemble the items I request immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a crude treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's the only option we have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold him down firmly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,as this will be a very delicate operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold him down firmly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll cause the Chakra to flow into his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will cause the toxin to surface from the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will then be absorbed by this liquid... and extracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the toxin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... Kakashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of person was that White Fang of the Leaf that this old lady here was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the son of the White Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course... So that's why you look so much like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I directly extracted the toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, his life should no longer be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still can't rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now concoct an antidote for traces of toxin that remain in his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need anything, don't hesitate to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, first, I need a list of the medicinal herbs that can be found in this village, or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please replace all of his bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then prepare an IV drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, please set aside a small amount of the extracted toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like the Slug Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that a girl just like you would come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Tsunade is my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, I was told by my master to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the list of medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Say Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is flowing slowly, but it's flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Takamaru has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baki, a reply has come from the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Granny Tsunade saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that Gai's squad has been sent here as a reinforcement unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bushy Brow sensei's squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet everyone has gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They even said that Neji has become a Jonin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Now's no time for us to just be hanging around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go after the Akatsuki... right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Going after them is fine and well...\NBut do you know where those guys have gone to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me for inquiring, but what is the follow-up to the Akatsuki pursuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Kankuro set off by himself and ended up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, a tracking unit was sent out, but they've yet to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the situation, it's likely that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the other village chiefs has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to think that he could be taken out so easily, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean to say you've completely lost sight of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro has awoken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're back already, Temari?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the village was in crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, don't talk such nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lead me to the place where Kankuro did battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it, but I'm a pro at tracking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If just the slightest trace of their scent remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My puppets... have all been recovered, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined I'd find this assortment of medicinal herbs here in the Hidden Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the soil is not well suited to growing medicinal herbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, we only have a small amount of "Scurvy Grass".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this much is plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make at least three antidotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy force was two in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them led Gaara away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is follow Gaara's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they split up into two, one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His smell is on that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On Crow's hand... I left him holding a scrap of his clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you fall, you won't fall without a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from a Sand ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he came all the way from the Hidden Leaf Village for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... Uzumaki... is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24\fad(200,200)}(Kuchiyose no Jutsu: Summoning Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kuchiyose no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight Ninja Dogs, at your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pakkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is that you, Naruto?! Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pakkun, you haven't changed a bit, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! I've grown quite a bit taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, but enough of this chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to get to work right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to determine which way he headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll contact you right away when we find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When Pakkun and the others get back, we're heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to make preparations right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo? Grandpa Ebizo, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear it one more time,\Ndirectly from your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mistake that one of the two enemies was Sasori, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it, Kankuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It was Sasori of the Red Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He said so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori of the Red Sand, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to find out more about Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to drink it all down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be all right now, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just lie there and rest for a while without moving until the numbness goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all get a good night's rest as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a room for you to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've got to find Gaara quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take advantage of you kindness, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going on a harsh march from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just have to work hard and carve out a future for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I must not run away from my path of solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I do that, someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someday... I can be like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's enough outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have never thought of you all as my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get in my way, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now there's something I understand about the bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he went so far to tell me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that pain, sadness... and happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...can be shared with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto Uzumaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned that through fighting and getting to know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He knew of the same pain as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he taught me that I could change the path of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto Uzumaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I am eventually going to become the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll do the Kazekage a favor early on!
